BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
a.  [`P \wedge Q\text{.}`]
a.  [`\newcommand{\imp}{\rightarrow}P \imp \neg Q\text{.}`]
a.  Jack passed math or Jill passed math (or both).

a.  If Jack and Jill did not both pass math, then Jill did.

a.  [$NBSP]*
    i.  Nothing else.
    i.  Jack did not pass math either.   

